{"tid":1857863,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［封關］林奠：唔封關，但會繼續聆聽，並透過討論釋除疑慮","createTime":"2020-02-02T11:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T12:31:01.000Z","uid":314803,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"00de4266874488105e5be4bb1e01dbfacc3e63b3","tid":1857863,"uid":314803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:15:53.000Z","msg":"過去一個月香港各界奮力面對新型冠狀病毒疫情，醫護人員守在最前線，一直緊守崗位，政府向他們致謝及致敬。<br />\n   <br />\n  政府明白醫護人員近日面對極大壓力，亦有醫護人員擔心病毒跨境傳播令公營醫療系統不勝負荷。政府認同管控關口和壓縮跨境人流的需要，並已<strong>盡全力</strong>推出減少人流的有關措施。然而，政府已多次詳細解釋提出不能全面封閉關口的原因。根據過去數星期的經驗，相關官員的親身解說有助消除這些誤解，因此政府會繼續接觸各方及聆聽，透過冷靜和理性的討論，釋除這些疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/02/P20200202000.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F02%2FP20200202000.htm&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9JriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=fdbd4bfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/02/P20200202000.htm</a>"},{"pid":"333585a94d4844911affd6ab9554c6640c611575","tid":1857863,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:16:33.000Z","msg":"聽妳老母好唔好 ?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bq70aOE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBq70aOE.jpg&h=84a3d903&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e2d244e9604261e2eaff95c48eb0a825307178f","tid":1857863,"uid":295548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:17:10.000Z","msg":"天滅中共賦"},{"pid":"55ab8364ec5275cd0d873022a280618195fa5592","tid":1857863,"uid":34235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:17:14.000Z","msg":"篇文冇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e84911e1d92d9d5e19e7ff42dff5844ee7e36bb","tid":1857863,"uid":21141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:17:32.000Z","msg":"Fake<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /