t.com%2F-S9eHE7CeDUg%2FW9qapeAjerI%2FAAAAAAAAA0c%2FuY37tj5pEUsf5DfeI7UF9rzVhcW6aAD2wCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F%2525E8%252583%2525A1%2525E6%25259D%25258F%2525E5%252585%252592%252B%2525E4%2525BD%2525A0%2525E8%252581%2525BD%2525E4%2525B8%25258B%2525E6%252588%252591%2525E8%2525A7%2525A3%2525E9%252587%25258B%2525E5%252585%252588%2525E5%252595%2525A6.jpg&h=0439182d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0014047c7eda9b63f73799dfe6983deda6cd6244","tid":1857863,"uid":288812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:58:16.000Z","msg":"《緊急》醫護手足做晒野，大陸文宣行動po呢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1857900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1857900</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b115916d79c04c8bdc22f4665226d6b866a810b6","tid":1857863,"uid":255333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:13:01.000Z","msg":"向醫護致敬喎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dm7TKyJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDm7TKyJ.jpg&h=6ea550c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cdc83d16482aae39a19fd7d310724ef12342d6c","tid":1857863,"uid":297045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b67b8367689ed7a397b24d98fc7c17c169dc343","tid":1857863,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:31:32.000Z","msg":"佢成日以為全世界都錯，係得佢正確，要講到人接受佢果套<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:16:30.000Z","msg":"同逃犯條例一樣, 初心正確, 只係因為解說唔夠而令市民誤解云云<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e91f8e3b697b44ebd382c1d48571066dbbcaa37","tid":1857863,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:19:10.000Z","msg":"政府回應傳媒查詢<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  就傳媒有關有醫護人員計劃罷工的查詢，政府發言人今日（二月二日）作以下回應。<br />\n   <br />\n  過去一個月香港各界奮力面對新型冠狀病毒疫情，醫護人員守在最前線，一直緊守崗位，政府向他們致謝及致敬。<br />\n   <br />\n  政府明白醫護人員近日面對極大壓力，亦有醫護人員擔心病毒跨境傳播令公營醫療系統不勝負荷。政府認同管控關口和壓縮跨境人流的需要，並已盡全力推出減少人流的有關措施，令包括香港居民、內地居民和外地旅客經各口岸抵港的人數大幅下降。政府正不斷檢視疫情，探討進一步管控關口。<br />\n   <br />\n  此外，為確保醫護人員在口罩等物資供應緊張時得到所需照顧，政府把醫護人員的需要列為首要考慮；醫院管理局亦改變了對非符合資格人士的收費政策。<br />\n<br />\n  現時是防控疫情的關鍵時刻，政府懇請各位打算參與罷工的醫護人員重新考慮，繼續以一貫的專業精神守護香港，戰勝這場疫情。<br />\n   <br />\n  政府知悉醫院管理局管理層今日稍後會與員工會面，聆聽員工的關注及商討解決方法。行政長官今日稍後亦會召開督導委員會暨指揮中心會議，研究如何防控疫情。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年2月2日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間0時16分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/02/P2020020200012.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F02%2FP2020020200012.htm&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9JriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=2d357257\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/02/P2020020200012.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">樓主FAKE NEWS?</span></strong></span><br />\n定佢偷偷改左?"},{"pid":"00d08bc0c3d2bb9a119b0c0e92139799302b31a1","tid":1857863,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:20:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同舊年6月9號晚嗰篇新聞稿一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"9ee74b5bd7721c6b8c9aebbff99b5368221e6b2b","tid":1857863,"uid":268342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:22:54.000Z","msg":"討論可令病毒死亡，係林鄭先想得到"},{"pid":"627342ee6ced1e197df38c279679bcefadff7e86","tid":1857863,"uid":277261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:31:01.000Z","msg":"唔封關而且要釋除這些疑慮<br />\n潛台詞就係我岩你錯<br />\n所以等我解釋你聽你錯咩<br />\n先可以釋除這些疑慮"}]}